title: Top 5 Christmas Skins of All Time - League of Legends

embed.description: Top 5 Christmas Skins of All Time - League of Legends==-- Hey guys! As it is the holiday seasons I thought I'd bring you all a Christmas themed video for all of you who celebrate it! I apologise if you do not agree with my list, but this is my opinion only and there are plenty of other amazing Christmas skins!

body:
Hey Everyone! I recently made this video on the top 5 Christmas skins of all time, (in my opinion) as we are currently in the holiday season. If you guys could check it out and give me some suggestions, that would be great. Be sure to leave a 'like' if you enjoyed, as it really helps me out, also, if you like my content be sure to subscribe, as I upload videos similar to this frequently! Maybe check out a few of my other videos, you may enjoy some of them! 

 - Anibaedan / Wekt
